    org.springframework.data.support.IsNewStrategyFactory

    public class MappingContextIsNewStrategyFactory
extends org.springframework.data.support.IsNewStrategyFactorySupport
    An IsNewStrategyFactory using a MappingContext to determine the IsNewStrategy to be returned for a particular type. It will look for a version and id property on the PersistentEntity and return a strategy instance that will reflectively inspect the property for null values or null or a value of 0 in case of a version property.
